{"body": [{"indent": 0, "text": ["Project"], "type": "title", "extent": [94, 106], "level": 0}, {"indent": 0, "type": "summary", "extent": [106, 150], "text": ["Creates profile curves on surfaces."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [150, 341], "text": ["The Project SOP creates profile curves (also known as trim curves\nor curves-on-surface) by projecting a 3D face onto a spline surface,\nmuch like a light casts a 2D shadow onto a 3D surface."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [341, 463], "text": ["There are two projection methods:\nalong a vector, or mapping the face directly onto the parametric\nspace of the surface."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [463, 511], "text": ["After a Project node you will often want to\u2026"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [511, 604], "text": ["Use a ", {"text": ["Trim SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/trim", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/trim"}, " to cut a hole in the projected surface\n  (as shown above)."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [604, 696], "text": ["Use a ", {"text": ["Bridge SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/bridge", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/bridge"}, " to skin the profile curve to\n  another profile curve."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [696, 793], "text": ["Use a ", {"text": ["Profile SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/profile", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/profile"}, " to extract the curve on surface\n  or remap its position."]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [793, 835], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/images/ProjectBasicView.jpg", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "../images/ProjectBasicView.jpg"}]}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [882, 1178], "text": ["To delete a projected curve, use a ", {"text": ["Delete SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/delete", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/delete"}, ", and\nenter the profile number (e.g. 1.4 returns the fifth profile on the\nsecond primitive (counting starts at 0) ). You can visualize the\nnumber of the profiles by enabling the Profile Number icon in the\nViewport Display options."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [1178, 1344], "text": ["You can group the profile curves with a ", {"text": ["Group SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/group", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/group"}, ".\nDo this by typing the profile numbers in the Pattern field. You can\nuse all regular expressions."]}, {"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [1344, 1566], "text": ["You can apply parametric affine transformations to the profile by\nusing a ", {"text": ["Primitive SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/primitive", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/primitive"}, ". You can also use the\n", {"text": ["Primitive SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/primitive", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/primitive"}, " to open, close, reverse, and\ncycle the profile curves."]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "type": "para", "extent": [1572, 1883], "text": ["When applying transformations to a profile in the ", {"text": ["Primitive\n    SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/primitive", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/primitive"}, ", you can only rotate about the Z axis\n    because the projected curve is a planar curve that lives in the\n    domain of the surface. Therefore it wouldn\u2019t make any sense to\n    allow rotations in X or Y for profiles."]}], "indent": 0, "role": "item", "type": "note", "extent": [1566, 1572]}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "note_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Additional Operations for Profile Curves"], "extent": [835, 882], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [1906, 2039], "text": ["Place a ", {"text": ["Circle SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/circle", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/circle"}, ", Type: NURBS, Radius 0.3,\n      0.3; then place a ", {"text": ["Tube SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/tube", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/tube"}, ", Type: NURBS."]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [2039, 2118], "text": ["Connect them into a Project op: Circle to Input1; Tube to\n      Input2."]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "ord", "extent": [2118, 2348], "text": ["Append a ", {"text": ["Trim SOP"], "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/trim", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/trim"}, " to the Project node. It\n      trims the surface according to the projection provided by the\n      Project node. You need to append a Trim node to a Project node\n      to get this trimming."]}, {"body": [{"indent": 6, "type": "para", "extent": [2454, 2500], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/images/Houdini-03-1-062.jpg", "scheme": "Image", "type": "link", "value": "../images/Houdini-03-1-062.jpg"}]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Turn on the template flags on the Circle and Tube nodes; make\n      the Project op the display op."], "extent": [2348, 2454], "blevel": 6, "type": "ord"}], "container": true, "type": "ord_group"}], "indent": 0, "tag": "steps", "attrs": {}, "extent": [1897, 1906], "type": "pxml"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Example"], "extent": [1883, 1897], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "type": "para", "extent": [2511, 2729], "text": ["The: Minimum Distance option is\nextremely useful, say in the following situation: You have a\nNURBS surface of a head, and you want to obtain a NURBS patch by\nprojecting a hairline onto the head\u2019s surface. You could:"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2729, 2757], "text": ["Template the NURBS head."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2757, 2835], "text": ["Enable the \"Snap to Template\" option in the Model Editor (Snap\n  options)."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2835, 2918], "text": ["Draw a NURBS curve along the surface of the head where you\n  want the hairline."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [2918, 3090], "text": ["Then, with the Project op, you select the Minimum Distance\n  option, and you have a profile curve with which you can trim\n  the surface of the head to obtain the patch."]}, {"indent": 0, "blevel": 2, "type": "bullet", "extent": [3090, 3253], "text": ["Thus having obtained a NURBS patch for the scalp, you could\n  use it as the source, say for the Emit pop to grow a particle\n  system in order to produce hair."]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 2, "text": ["Tips"], "extent": [2500, 2511], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [3281, 3341], "text": ["Subset of faces (NURBS,Bezier,polygons) to project."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Face Group"], "role": "item", "extent": [3265, 3281], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [3360, 3409], "text": ["Subset of spline surfaces to project on."]}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Surface Group"], "role": "item", "extent": [3341, 3360], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 8, "type": "para", "extent": [3425, 3484], "text": ["Ways of choosing projection order and sequencing:"]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [3531, 3572], "text": ["In the given domain interval"]}], "indent": 8, "type": "dt", "extent": [3484, 3531], "text": ["All faces on each surface in sequence"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [3619, 3660], "text": ["In the given domain interval"]}], "indent": 8, "type": "dt", "extent": [3572, 3619], "text": ["All faces on each surface overlapping"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [3706, 3799], "text": ["One face per surface, cycled until all surfaces have been\n            traversed"]}], "indent": 8, "type": "dt", "extent": [3660, 3706], "text": ["One face per surface:\n        Cycled"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 4, "text": ["Cycle Type"], "role": "item", "extent": [3409, 3425], "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [3841, 3891], "text": ["Faces are projected along a 3D vector"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Overview"], "role": "item", "extent": [3822, 3841], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [3905, 4028], "text": ["Vector along which to project the faces: X, Y, Z,\n            user-defined, or minimum distance to the surface"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Axis"], "role": "item", "extent": [3891, 3905], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4098, 4148], "text": ["x,y,z components of projection vector"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Vector"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/projvec1 /projvec2 /projvec3"}, "extent": [4028, 4044], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4162, 4224], "text": ["What side of the surface to project the face on:"]}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "extent": [4245, 4311], "text": ["On the first side encountered in either direction"]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "extent": [4224, 4245], "text": ["Closest"]}, {"body": [{"indent": 16, "type": "para", "extent": [4333, 4398], "text": ["On the last side encountered in either direction"]}], "indent": 12, "type": "dt", "extent": [4311, 4333], "text": ["Farthest"]}], "container": true, "type": "dt_group"}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Side"], "role": "item", "extent": [4148, 4162], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4457, 4512], "text": ["Number of 3D points evaluated in each span"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Divisions Per Span"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/sdivs"}, "extent": [4398, 4426], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4571, 4621], "text": ["Precision of ray-surface intersection"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Ray Tolerance"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/rtolerance"}, "extent": [4512, 4535], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4680, 4726], "text": ["Precision of 2D fitting algorithm"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Fit Tolerance"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/ftolerance"}, "extent": [4621, 4644], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4781, 4833], "text": ["Percentage of domain to join 2 profiles"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Max UV Gap (%)"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/uvgap"}, "extent": [4726, 4750], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4879, 4931], "text": ["Spline order of resulting profile curve"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Order"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/order"}, "extent": [4833, 4848], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [4963, 5025], "text": ["Enable or disable fitting of sharp turns in curve"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Preserve Sharp Corners"], "role": "item", "extent": [4931, 4963], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5049, 5112], "text": ["Use a very accurate, yet time consuming algorithm"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Super Accurate"], "role": "item", "extent": [5025, 5049], "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Along Vector"], "extent": [3799, 3822], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}, {"body": [{"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5156, 5213], "text": ["Direct conversion of 3D CVs to domain points"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Overview"], "role": "item", "extent": [5137, 5156], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5229, 5290], "text": ["Which of X,Y,Z must be mapped to the U parameter"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["U From"], "role": "item", "extent": [5213, 5229], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5306, 5367], "text": ["Which of X,Y,Z must be mapped to the V parameter"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["V From"], "role": "item", "extent": [5290, 5306], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5397, 5458], "text": ["Constrain the profile to the domain range below:"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Map Profile to Range"], "role": "item", "extent": [5367, 5397], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5517, 5571], "text": ["Area of the unit U domain to be mapped on"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["U Range"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/urange1 /urange2"}, "extent": [5458, 5475], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5630, 5684], "text": ["Area of the unit V domain to be mapped on"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["V Range"], "role": "item", "attrs": {"channels": "/vrange1 /vrange2"}, "extent": [5571, 5588], "type": "parameters_item"}, {"body": [{"indent": 12, "type": "para", "extent": [5706, 5760], "text": ["Uniform or chord length based conversion"]}], "indent": 8, "text": ["Mapping Type"], "role": "item", "extent": [5684, 5706], "type": "parameters_item"}], "container": true, "role": "item_group", "type": "parameters_item_group"}], "indent": 4, "level": 2, "text": ["Parametrically"], "extent": [5112, 5137], "container": true, "type": "h", "id": null}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Parameters", "role": "section", "extent": [3253, 3265], "container": true, "type": "parameters_section", "id": "parameters"}, {"body": [{"body": [{"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [5769, 5791], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/trim", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/trim"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [5791, 5816], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/profile", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/profile"}]}, {"indent": 4, "blevel": 6, "type": "bullet", "extent": [5816, 5844], "text": [{"text": "", "fullpath": "/nodes/sop/primitive", "scheme": "Node", "type": "link", "value": "/nodes/sop/primitive"}]}], "container": true, "type": "bullet_group"}], "indent": 0, "level": 1, "text": "Related", "role": "section", "extent": [5760, 5769], "container": true, "type": "related_section", "id": "related"}], "summary": ["Creates profile curves on surfaces."], "type": "root", "attrs": {"version": null, "tags": "project, trim, model", "namespace": null, "internal": "project", "context": "sop", "type": "node", "icon": "SOP/project"}, "title": ["Project"]}